thread.title: Emily Gerard

author: Emily Gerard
title: Emily Gerard
text: Rachel Crocker helped us from the moment we were interested in doing a transaction, we were so confused and didn't know what we were doing and she made it so easy, we were worried we wouldn't get our money due to a public holiday and she even rang us on the Tuesday to double check we got it ok. Great service and we saved around $1000 from not tranfering with our bank. Thanks again Rachel!
